Name: Poison
Description: A viscous, dangerous-looking concoction. This can be used to poison food and drink, or rubbed into a weapon. Creatures exposed to this poison must succeed on a Constitution saving throw (DC=DAMAGE10-20DAMAGE) or succumb to its effects, taking half damage (where applicable) and no other effect on a successful save. If used to augment a weapon, the next TIME1-5TIME attacks made with the weapon apply the effect(s) below. If ingested, the poison lasts for TIME1-10TIME minutes or TIME1-8TIME hours (DM's discretion).
Requirements: None
